{"tid":1594753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求你地相信，義士鬼魂既存在","createTime":"2019-09-25T16:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T06:40:48.000Z","uid":149545,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d2e3cd5a097241ad9022e7a1527698e76f1986a6","tid":1594753,"uid":149545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:59:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LjBypvRnJZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLjBypvRnJZ4&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=54e54b51\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LjBypvRnJZ4</a><br />\n<br />\n各位<br />\n希望大家可以用一個開放既態度去理解，如果你信有鬼，亦都應該相信中共用好多法術風水殘害香港！<br />\n<br />\n片段中有人講到包括太子站義士既鬼魂，中共用法術害港等等，當中包括寶蓮寺，西九其實係中共害港既風水等等，希望大定聽聽<br />\n<br />\n有D野，我諗唔到你唔信，風水鬼神亦都有非常多個案去影響一個人或地方，所以我希望大家可以為呢場抗爭，增加多一份可能，或者可以多一份勝算。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以用一個開放既態度去睇睇呢件事，多謝大家。"},{"pid":"77111a423ede51df0948568b38cdda46e6322309","tid":1594753,"uid":12662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:03:09.000Z","msg":"「置頂」 停止跳閘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594440\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1594440</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4150fff8606947311d06b8bee468b00b983a55fa","tid":1594753,"uid":149545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"130d767e680dfbfa6074e9050227eb1ab305bb96","tid":1594753,"uid":149545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:04:02.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"4681ca7cca86e6ac48b6f5a8004edc4f2c8d176a","tid":1594753,"uid":62167,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:04:20.000Z","msg":"風水術數真係好難接受"},{"pid":"c0a7b83478f03a1c075a1855a1466b5c59436cdb","tid":1594753,"uid":149545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4681ca7cca86e6ac48b6f5a8004edc4f2c8d176a","tid":1594753,"uid":62167,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T17:04:20.000Z","msg":"風水術數真係好難接受"},"cite